{"detail": {"project_id": 157698, "id": 157698, "user_id": 497142, "name": "NOVEMBRO VOL. 2", "headline": "O lugar errado. A hora errada. As mulheres certas para revidar.", "budget": "<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448834/f690b1ac-22fa-466b-9a93-2df505a2ce69.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p>O or\u00e7amento do projeto est\u00e1 dividido da seguinte forma:\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Impress\u00e3o</strong> \u2013 Da HQ <em><strong>Novembro Vol. II - o Rev\u00f3lver na Po\u00e7a</strong></em>, dos marcadores de p\u00e1ginas e das poss\u00edveis metas estendidas. Os demais quadrinhos j\u00e1 publicados pela <strong>Editora Risco</strong> n\u00e3o est\u00e3o inclu\u00eddos nesta equa\u00e7\u00e3o.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Edi\u00e7\u00e3o</strong> \u2013 Inclui os custos dos <em>royalties</em> de licenciamento, arquivos, tradu\u00e7\u00e3o, letras, projeto gr\u00e1fico e diagrama\u00e7\u00e3o. Todos j\u00e1 efetuados pela editora.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Envios</strong> \u2013 Aquisi\u00e7\u00e3o de caixas/envelopes e etiquetas, manuseio e envio dos pacotes via Correios na modalidade registro m\u00f3dico.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Catarse</strong> \u2013 Taxa cobrada das campanhas hospedadas na plataforma.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448835/c8d416df-cdb1-48f7-afd2-e2be9cc5c80e.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Confira abaixo o cronograma da campanha:</strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Outubro</strong> \u2013 Encerramento da campanha, diagrama\u00e7\u00e3o e aprova\u00e7\u00e3o final do material junto ao licenciante.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Novembro</strong> \u2013 Produ\u00e7\u00e3o das metas estendidas e revis\u00e3o final. Impress\u00e3o da HQ (aprova\u00e7\u00e3o do boneco do livro, das cores da capa, sobrecapa e miolo) e recebimento do lote em nosso estoque.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Dezembro</strong> \u2013 Confirma\u00e7\u00e3o de endere\u00e7o dos apoiadores e envio de todas as recompensas.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448836/2a3b00ea-f91e-45f3-83ea-96c216535cc4.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>", "goal": 12000.0, "about_html": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong></strong>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448827/fcfb32dd-c5f2-4c7b-9fc6-7c92028658fb.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Di</strong> aceita um trabalho f\u00e1cil e lucrativo demais para ser honesto. <strong>Emma</strong> encontra um rev\u00f3lver em um beco. <strong>Kowalski</strong> decide investigar o que est\u00e1 acontecendo de errado em sua delegacia. Enquanto explos\u00f5es, fogo e viol\u00eancia tomam conta da cidade no curso de um dia e uma noite, as tr\u00eas mulheres veem suas vidas entrela\u00e7adas, ligadas por conta de um homem \u2013 que parece ser o causador de tudo isso.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/447786/cbd5b200-d9b7-452b-bcdf-12ef2313f873.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">De volta ao <i>noir</i>, <strong>Matt Fraction</strong> se une a <strong>Elsa Charretier </strong>na cria\u00e7\u00e3o de uma trama s\u00f3rdida, que levar\u00e1 suas personagens ao extremo.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448826/a6760323-d55d-4fed-9052-fff700aede05.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><strong>Novembro</strong></em> \u00e9 uma miniss\u00e9rie em quatro volumes do g\u00eanero de suspense policial. Publicada originalmente nos EUA entre 2019 e 2021 pela <strong>Image Comics</strong>, chega ao Brasil agora pela <strong>Risco Editora</strong>. Confira abaixo o cronograma para os lan\u00e7amentos de cada um dos quatro volumes da s\u00e9rie.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/447787/72330ffd-1402-4f22-8e97-cc3917dd16ee.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Toda a s\u00e9rie \u00e9 publicada em formato americano (17x26cm), capa cart\u00e3o com verniz localizado e 80 p\u00e1ginas coloridas.<br>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448825/64c10e6d-278c-466e-82c4-8d8e6289f1a7.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/447788/1083561c-8532-4560-8cd0-fe7550336515.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1JAHl61G4d0CSvkJAwtmKaUzGBwoQgz3m/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">Confira aqui o <em>preview</em> de <em>Novembro Vol. II: o Rev\u00f3lver na Po\u00e7a</em>.</a> </strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/447789/cc9d3510-3dad-417c-b354-0bff4132fa68.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\"></span></strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QGWf4haoitpZmab-VdRMWZntUF2ieARO/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">Confira aqui o <em>preview</em> de <em>Novembro Vol. I: a Garota do Telhado</em>.</a> </span></strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><em><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448824/0e128e3a-b4c1-45c6-a3a0-7bf69c48beed.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\"></em></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong><em><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/447791/d2ba7c5c-589d-45b1-9a6b-eb831ae44f0b.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\"></em></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MATT FRACTION - Autor/Roteirista<br></strong>Famoso por seus trabalhos para a <strong>Marvel Comics</strong>, com destaque para sua parceria com o desenhista <strong>David Aja</strong> em <em><strong>Gavi\u00e3o Arqueiro</strong></em> \u2013 que serviu de base para a miniss\u00e9rie da <strong>Disney+</strong> \u2013 al\u00e9m da s\u00e9rie em quadrinhos <i><strong>Criminosos do Sexo</strong></i>, Matt Fraction acumula trof\u00e9us e indica\u00e7\u00f5es \u00e0s mais importantes premia\u00e7\u00f5es dos quadrinhos, como o <strong>Eisner Award</strong> e o <strong>Harvey Award</strong>.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>ELSA CHARRETIER - Autora/Artista<br></strong>Autodidata, assina a arte de t\u00edtulos importantes das principais editoras norte americanas, como <em><strong>Star Wars</strong></em> e <em><strong>The Unstoppable Wasp</strong></em> pela <strong>Marvel Comics</strong> e <em><strong>The Infinite Loop</strong></em> pela <strong>IDW</strong>, a francesa Elsa Charretier d\u00e1 a perfeita atmosfera <i>noir</i> \u00e0 hist\u00f3ria, com um tra\u00e7o que valoriza as emo\u00e7\u00f5es e express\u00f5es de cada personagem. Elsa \u00e9 uma das indicadas ao <strong>Harvey Award</strong> deste ano com a <em>webcomic</em> <em><strong>Love Everlasting</strong></em>, que conta com roteiros do <strong>Tom King</strong>. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ElsaCharretierChannel\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Conhe\u00e7a o canal da Elsa no Youtube</strong></a>.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong></strong>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448854/0819729d-3911-4a46-84e0-3b350c37d936.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>COLORIZA\u00c7\u00c3O<br></strong>O premiado colorista <strong>Matt Hollingsworth</strong> completa o time de artistas com sua paleta de cores minimalista, perfeitas para o clima sombrio e misterioso da HQ.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448855/ea29892c-be1d-422f-831f-ce8fb0077a0b.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>LETREIRAMENTO<br></strong>Na edi\u00e7\u00e3o original, o ilustrador e tip\u00f3grafo <strong>Kurt Ankeny</strong> utiliza t\u00e9cnicas de escrita manual para dar voz \u00e0s protagonistas, criando \"tipos\" distintos para cada uma delas. Pensando nos m\u00ednimos detalhes, encomendamos ao consagrado letrista <strong>Arion Wu</strong> quatro fontes desenvolvidas a partir da caligrafia de Ankeny para a edi\u00e7\u00e3o da Risco Editora, que conta com o balonamento do <strong>Gabriel Calfa</strong>.\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448856/cde8b760-1711-4d41-b065-2f40ae8fad7e.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448823/9ef38739-c6e9-494a-8499-24589a162d5c.png\" style=\"display:block;margin:auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Criada em 2016, a <a href=\"https://www.riscoeditora.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>RISC\u00d8</strong></a> come\u00e7ou focada exclusivamente na produ\u00e7\u00e3o de quadrinhos originais, com os roteiros dos s\u00f3cios <strong>Gabriel Calfa</strong><strong></strong> e <strong>Marcus Leopoldino</strong> em parceria com diversos artistas da cena independente de quadrinhos. A partir de 2021 decidimos dar um passo diferente e tornar a Risco uma editora tamb\u00e9m de obras licenciadas internacionais, e come\u00e7amos a pesquisar t\u00edtulos que tivessem a nossa cara, tanto cl\u00e1ssicos como novidades, europeus, estadunidenses e sul-americanos.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Como f\u00e3s de hist\u00f3rias <em>noir</em> que somos, escolhemos <em><strong>Novembro</strong></em> para ser a primeira miniss\u00e9rie que publicamos desta nova fase. Admiramos muito o trabalho do <strong>Fraction</strong> em diferentes g\u00eaneros e atrav\u00e9s deste t\u00edtulo em especial fomos apresentados ao maravilhoso trabalho da <strong>Elsa Charretier</strong>. Temos certeza que <em><strong>Novembro</strong></em> ser\u00e1 um deleite para os nossos leitores!\n</p>\n<blockquote class=\"fontsize-base quote\">Convidamos voc\u00eas a fazerem parte desta nova fase da <a href=\"https://www.riscoeditora.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Risco Editora</strong></a>!<br><br><img src=\"https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/redactor_rails/picture/data/448858/c50b1259-f0ba-4937-91c6-76de4edbaccb.png\">\n</blockquote>", "permalink": "novembro2", "video_embed_url": null, "video_url": null, "category_name": "Quadrinhos", "category_id": 7, "original_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/project/uploaded_image/157698/7bfc3a9d-f6eb-4eec-b81d-d89d90e0405c.png", "thumb_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/project/uploaded_image/157698/project_thumb_thumb_7bfc3a9d-f6eb-4eec-b81d-d89d90e0405c.png", "small_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/project/uploaded_image/157698/project_thumb_small_7bfc3a9d-f6eb-4eec-b81d-d89d90e0405c.png", "large_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/project/uploaded_image/157698/project_thumb_large_7bfc3a9d-f6eb-4eec-b81d-d89d90e0405c.png", "video_cover_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/project/uploaded_image/157698/project_thumb_video_cover_7bfc3a9d-f6eb-4eec-b81d-d89d90e0405c.png", "progress": 69.33333333333333, "pledged": 8320.0, "total_contributions": 121, "total_contributors": 120, "state": "successful", "mode": "flex", "state_order": "finished", "expires_at": "2022-10-28T02:59:59.999999", "zone_expires_at": "2022-10-27T23:59:59.999999", "online_date": "2022-09-27T09:24:51.9635", "zone_online_date": "2022-09-27T06:24:51.9635", "sent_to_analysis_at": null, "is_published": true, "is_expired": true, "open_for_contributions": false, "online_days": 30, "remaining_time": {"total": 0, "unit": "seconds"}, "elapsed_time": {"total": 30, "unit": "days"}, "posts_count": 5, "address": {"city": "Niter\u00f3i", "state_acronym": "RJ", "state": "Rio de Janeiro"}, "user": {"id": 497142, "name": "MARCUS MARCELLO PORTO LEOPOLDINO 09933276727", "public_name": "RISCO EDITORA"}, "reminder_count": 104, "is_owner_or_admin": null, "user_signed_in": false, "in_reminder": false, "total_posts": 5, "can_request_transfer": true, "is_admin_role": false, "contributed_by_friends": false, "admin_tag_list": null, "tag_list": "Bechdel,Noir,Suspense", "city_id": 3642, "admin_notes": null, "service_fee": 0.13, "has_cancelation_request": false, "can_cancel": false, "tracker_snippet_html": null, "cover_image": null, "common_id": "58adb761-5719-4fd6-b293-00a5a57c2df6", "is_adult_content": false, "content_rating": 1, "recommended": true, "integrations": []}, "user": {"id": 497142, "common_id": "c3a4abd3-060c-4931-99c0-a7a71fcc9f1e", "name": "MARCUS MARCELLO PORTO LEOPOLDINO 09933276727", "deactivated_at": null, "profile_img_thumbnail": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/user/uploaded_image/497142/thumb_avatar_d649e047-8097-4b31-8860-db30c3044c06.png", "facebook_link": "http://www.facebook.com/riscoeditora", "twitter_username": "riscoeditora", "address": null, "email": null, "total_contributed_projects": 11, "total_published_projects": 20, "links": [{"id": 40837, "link": "http://www.instagram.com/riscoeditora"}, {"id": 7642, "link": "https://www.riscoeditora.com"}], "follows_count": 16, "followers_count": 642, "owner_document": null, "profile_cover_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/user/cover_image/497142/base_6b62df2a-b460-4b61-a255-09abd3ab649f.png", "created_at": "2015-11-13T16:26:02.291876", "about_html": "<p>A RISC\u00d8 \u00e9 uma editora independente focada na publica\u00e7\u00e3o de hist\u00f3rias em quadrinhos. Administrada pelos s\u00f3cios Gabriel Calfa e Marcus Leopoldino, seus trabalhos iniciaram no ano de 2016 publicando material original de seus criadores em parceria com diversos artistas.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Gabriel \u00e9 publicit\u00e1rio, roteirista e editor de quadrinhos. Seu hist\u00f3rico como diretor de arte o credencia a ser o respons\u00e1vel pelo design e diagrama\u00e7\u00e3o de todas nossas publica\u00e7\u00f5es. Nada passa despercebido a seu olhar atento.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Marcus \u00e9 psic\u00f3logo, roteirista e editor de quadrinhos. F\u00e3 de fic\u00e7\u00e3o cient\u00edfica e fantasia, sempre em busca de uma forma de unir estes g\u00eaneros em suas cria\u00e7\u00f5es. Est\u00e1 a cargo da prepara\u00e7\u00e3o de textos e contratos.\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A RISC\u00d8 passeia por diferentes g\u00eaneros da fic\u00e7\u00e3o buscando sempre entregar ao leitor qualidade e sentimento com seus t\u00edtulos. Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 convidado a conhecer nossas publica\u00e7\u00f5es e viver todo esse mundo novo de hist\u00f3rias.\n</p>", "is_owner_or_admin": null, "newsletter": false, "subscribed_to_project_posts": false, "subscribed_to_new_followers": true, "subscribed_to_friends_contributions": false, "is_admin": false, "permalink": null, "email_active": null, "public_name": "RISCO EDITORA", "following_this_user": false, "state_inscription": null, "birth_date": null, "account_type": null, "is_admin_role": false, "mail_marketing_lists": null}, "rewards": [{"id": 278623, "project_id": 157698, "description": "Novembro Vol. II com 20% de desconto\n+ Novembro Vol. I com 20% de desconto\n+ Marcador de p\u00e1ginas\n+ Nome na lista de apoiadores\n\nFrete de R$ 12 adicionado ao fim da opera\u00e7\u00e3o.", "minimum_value": 88.0, "maximum_contributions": null, "deliver_at": "2022-12-01T21:47:28", "updated_at": "2022-09-29T13:53:24.624097", "paid_count": 13, "waiting_payment_count": 0, "shipping_options": "national", "row_order": 1006632960, "title": "NOVEMBRO I & II - 20% OFF", "survey_sent_at": "2023-01-17T15:14:56.765651", "survey_finished_at": "2023-12-12T18:27:13.069498", "common_id": "6805367d-5909-44ae-86fe-92f4850ba4ee", "welcome_message_subject": "", "welcome_message_body": "", "uploaded_image": "https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/cdn.br.catarse/uploads/reward/uploaded_image/278623/thumb_reward_81567c50-fac0-4735-9aad-5cb35d8318c7.png", "run_out": true}]}